result.title: Applied Machine Learning Engineer
result.description:
Position Description
- Propose machine learning initiatives to fuel our business growth, build an end to end machine learning framework/solution to improve our KPI/metrics
‍

Job Requirements
- 3+ years of experience in designing and implementing machine learning algorithms, and applying them to real-world problems
- Solid Machine Learning background and deep understanding of the certain domain of machine learning techniques, especially in natural language processing, recommendation systems, computer visions
